Source for first tweet: https://twitter.com/hogan698/status/1497291283106250761</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9sa3Vlw</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[truthsmiles]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Please forward this to anyone yo know in Ukraine or bordering states.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/3vPlCWL</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yBlibPQ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If you can translate this for Ukrainians, please do! This very hour. If you know friends in Ukraine, or even nearby states like Poland or Moldova, please send this to them, asking them to pass it along to any Ukrainians they know. Do it now.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/so8S4Nu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6CNWZLE.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uWC38Ws.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GQgGco0.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MfNCUVE.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1nYqCm6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>EDIT: weaken roads from underneath in sewers, make ditches too big for tanks to span, put fake IEDs with wires in potholes to force an unarmored crew to come investigate. And thermite in a can with a fuse and with glue or magnets on the exterior. And: accept surrender wherever possible.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/3vPlCWL</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jasonPositivityPilot]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Because he’s very tough, and not super fragile and thin-skinned…</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/lG2u2UG</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PAo2z2F.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/lG2u2UG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DaniusJones123]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sanction Fox, and sanction Carlson until he is removed from the air.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/XUJeqev</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/30Bx0xv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Tucker Carlson openly supports Vladimir Putin, and his criminal acts of war against a free and sovereign nation; while at the same time denigrating with malice his own President of the United States Joe Biden. Tucker Carlson is a traitor to United States democracy and must be removed from the air.

To anyone thinking, this isn't how a free society deals with a person's opinion. Under other circumstances you are right, but Carlson's views are broadcast and used by Russian state media to direct the narrative of their war crimes. Carlson knows this yet remains complicit in providing them with sound bytes. Carlson is using his platform to aid the enemy in illegal activities. This activity is flagrant malice as well and can be brought to court.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/XUJeqev</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheResolver]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>True love</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/HPMsg10</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UtFCnnW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/HPMsg10</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vidadobl6]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Beep beep!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0fIh3JN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V7A26i1.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0fIh3JN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AjKaramba]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>#</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vjoFyWO</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Z7EUVLM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vjoFyWO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Kira Rudik member of Parliament</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/lODhGDv</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zkS7obg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#ukraine #badass</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/lODhGDv</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jaysyn1980]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>No captions needed</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/rrBfYHH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e8VVEXg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/rrBfYHH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[6uffoonjiffy777]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Meet kyiv vitali klitschko. he is the mayor of kyiv and former heavyweight champion of the world. klitschko is a millionaire many times over, he could have fled ukraine by private jet and lived a happy life, but instead he decided to risk his own life and</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/T8ya1cO</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MSuYGM1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/T8ya1cO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[6ALDRICGlom926]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Shout out to the luckiest timeline 4 wp</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CvbKN4g</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MtC1qNp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CvbKN4g</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[0xymoronnadir287]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I've struggled how to put this into words, but here is some vital information about the situation in Ukraine</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/odjqckM</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7ll5Mlj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I've seen so many posts and comments about the situation in Ukraine, and I have been so distraught about most of the posts/comments involving the situation that I feel like I need to say something.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zpMj4ov.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>From everything that I know and what I believe, Ukrainians are some of the fiercest fighters out there and will protect their homeland with everything they have. Men, Women, and everyday citizens will take up arms to defend their home country... their livelihoods.... to repel Putin and his bullshit army</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Jm8cwgB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>What you're seeing in these pictures may seem like inexperienced people that will fold easily when Russian troops roll in, but I see some of the strongest people I've ever seen in my life.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qrbZAGq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Imagine your country, your state, your city coming under attack by a foreign military that is trying to take away everything that you love. You're beloved country now in disarray.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BI4i2DC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I know that a lot of people are asking "Why isn't NATO doing more to help out"? The direct answer is.... they can't. NATO is a defensive collaboration between countries under a pact, and the unfortunate fact is, Ukraine is not part of it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GTMzk9S.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Ukraine has been seeking membership with NATO, and that's why Putin is so upset with Ukraine right now. Russia sees Ukraine joining NATO as a direct threat to Russia. Now, this makes no sense, being that Ukraine is only seeking protection from countries like Russia (kind of a Catch 22)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WgBVGip.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A lot of people are wondering why the US military doesn't just go in and stomp the shit out of the Russian military. Well, this would lead to all out war with multiple Nations armed with Nuclear weapons.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vc4lBXg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Vladimir Putin is an extremely unstable person at the moment, and there's no telling what he would do if he's trapped in a corner. Nuclear war has no winners... we all die or suffer long lasting repercussions</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7F8w1id.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Now is the time to stand with Ukraine. Almost every country in the world is on Ukraine's side. Ukrainians know more than all of us, that they are in this fight primarily by themselves. We will provide as much ammunition, weapon systems, and intelligence as we can, but nuclear war is not something that can be risked</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/k2EuX2k.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I know that a lot of people don't think that sanctions do anything, but the Russian economy is feeling the pain. The ruble is at it's lowest value in a long time, and this is just the beginning.... Sanctions take time to show the real effect, but they are effective</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rYNOdHC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>F1 Grand Prix has been canceled in Russia, and this is just the start.... Nobody will want to be involved with Russia after what they've done... Russia will be ostracized from the world venue for all revenues</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5X8F2kD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The Russian people don't want this either. This is the desperate act of a failing leader</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qyN9EIY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'm not a religious person, but pray for our Ukrainian friends, brothers, and sisters fighting the good fight... fighting for their country!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/odjqckM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[parknasty913]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Animals in Panorama mode</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Ifcimml</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iS4zr72.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6fiCjVU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2CXUKlm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kkdxIik.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nkLUMAd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7A0617V.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oKBlNLj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MyMDkON.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/68X5tLS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bf0yspY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/W4RJXOF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/q11Tom2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RuLhj2v.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/N1kaIrh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><im